3.7 Putting it together
Each step above modified hartford and saved it back. We can write that entire chain as one pipeline:

hartford &lt;-
  covid_data |&gt;
  filter(Town == "Hartford") |&gt;
  select(
    date = `Last update date`,
    town = Town,
    new_positives = `Number of positives`,
    total_cases = `Total cases`,
    total_deaths = `Total deaths`
  ) |&gt;
  mutate(date = parse_date(date, format = "%m/%d/%Y")) |&gt;
  arrange(date)
